Description:
    Generates a rio js application.

Examples:

    ./script/generate rio_app todo

    will create:

		public/javascripts/apps/todo.js
	    public/stylesheets/todo.css
	    public/javascripts/pages/todo_page.js
	    public/javascripts/pages/todo_page.jst
	    public/stylesheets/todo_page.css
	    public/javascripts/apps/todo.build
	    app/controllers/rio_controller.rb
	    app/views/layouts/rio.html.erb
	    app/views/rio
	    app/views/rio/todo.html.erb
